FOOT & MOUTH DISEASE, CONFIRMED - JAPAN
***************************************
A ProMED-mail post
<http://www.promedmail.org>
See Also
Foot & mouth disease, suspected - Japan & S. Korea 20000328234118
Foot & mouth disease, suspected - Japan & S. Korea... 20000403225719
